---
title: Easy Caribbean Beef-Chorizo Chilli & Jacket Potatoes with Cheddar & Corn Slaw
description: Jacket potatoes are already the most dapper of potatoes, but you can never be too dapper. Jazz them up with a saucy beef and chorizo chilli, dressed in Caribbean seasoning and accessorised with Cheddar cheese. This dinner is sure to out dazzle all the other potatoes.
